message.body: I miss you. When the day is slow I get anxious about the time passing because all I want to do is be in your arms.
I miss you too. I can't wait to have you in my arms tonight :)
I love you. Haha. I love to hear things like that. I was actually just humming Babylon! I feel like we're going to see her instead of jhene. It should be good. I'm excited.
Haha no I'm going to see my girl, Jhen√©
I'm on my way to you. I'm waiting for the L.
